snippet.title: Banjo Kazooie Legend of the Crystal Jiggy Release Trailer
snippet.description:
After months of working on this it's finally out! It may not be perfect and I'm still not the most skilled at this so keep an open mind on things here, this still is a mod of the original banjo kazooie after all and we are still limited on a lot of stuff. But either way I hope you guys still enjoy it!

Join my Discord: https://discord.gg/7DYXuUv

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/g13jackson?lang=en

Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jacksong13yt

Download Patch: https://gamejolt.com/@JacksonG13
